{"tid":1106134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[14/4/2019] Facebook, Instagram, and WhatsApp 又 死機，down 咗","createTime":"2019-04-14T11:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T11:44:21.000Z","uid":103156,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d04f88d1189a82083ab7398c8659ffc6229abdca","tid":1106134,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:32:53.000Z","msg":"Facebook, Instagram, and WhatsApp are down for users around the world<br />\n6:30AM ET<br />\nApr 14, 2019, 7:12am EDT <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/4/14/18310069/facebook-instagram-whatsapp-down-outage-issues\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2019%2F4%2F14%2F18310069%2Ffacebook-instagram-whatsapp-down-outage-issues&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=74bbb413\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2019/4/14/18310069/facebook-instagram-whatsapp-down-outage-issues</a>"},{"pid":"697a3666aca9564d844dab2102c9f605812f43db","tid":1106134,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp及FB與IG全球大規模故障 港用戶受影響<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1479444/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1479444%2F&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=8a5be75e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1479444%2F&h=dc5cb1b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1479444/</a><br />\n<br />\n社交網站Facebook、即時通訊程式Facebook Messenger、Whatsapp以及社交網站Instagram，在香港時間傍晚6時起先後發生大規模故障，包括香港在內多個國家地區都無法瀏覽。外國傳媒報道，故障是由於技術問題導致。<br />\n<br />\n香港部分用戶在傍晚近7時一度恢復服務，但其後用戶再度未能瀏覽Facebook及Instagram的網頁版。<br />\n<br />\n據網上統計資料顯示，三大平台報告故障的宗數自傍晚6時起大幅飆升，其中歐洲屬於重災區，美洲及亞太區都有受影響。而三大平台均屬於Facebook同一集團。"},{"pid":"07415cf3daf3978a1e4c0d455e47beee001cc3a1","tid":1106134,"uid":11382,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:44:21.000Z","msg":"又黎料，仲以為個router打柴"}]}